THI OF NEW MEXICO AT CASA ARENA BLANCA, LLC, d/b/a Casa Arena Blanca Nursing Home, petitioner,
v.
Didier L. FIGUEROA, Individually and as Personal Representative for the Estate of Dolores Figueroa, Deceased. No. 12-1029. Supreme Court of the United States May 28, 2013.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of New Mexico denied.
